The paper discusses the security of IoT devices and proposes a novel approach for detecting intrusions in smart spaces using machine learning techniques. This topic falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and networked systems (cs.NI). The use of machine learning also suggests a potential fit for artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) categories. Finally, the paper also discusses the feasibility of the proposed approach under real-life conditions, which could be relevant to software engineering (cs.SE).
